description: Database of the laws of Estonia
label: Elektrooniline Riigi Teataja
title: Elektrooniline_Riigi_Teataja
exrest: Elektrooniline Riigi Teataja is the web-based outlet for publication of laws and official announcements of the Republic of Estonia. It is modelled after the older paper-based publication, Riigi Teataja. Under Estonian law, Elektrooniline Riigi Teataja is since 1 June 2002 considered the authoritative reference source for laws of Estonia. Just like Riigi Teataja, eRT is published by Riigikantselei.
